This function will return the name as a string of the specified script. This name is the one that has been specified for the script in the Asset Browser of the main GameMaker Studio 2 window. For more information about scripts, see The Script Editor.
The index of the script that you want to get the name of.
The above example code will store the name of the indicated script index in the variable "scr_name".
